profile:
Xolar is a full service turn-key platform for transitioning residential clients to solar energy. We support our clients with our done-for-you approach, taking you all the way from project design to construction.  We have completed projects all over Ontario, and have many happy customers.  Our customer referral program allows your system to pay for itself in more ways than one.

Visit our website at www.xolar.ca
Check out our work on instagram @xolar.energy
